articles.title: Indian women beat Thailand 5-4 in Asian Hockey 5s World Cup Qualifier - The Indian Express
articles.description: For India, skipper Navjot Kaur (1st minute), Monika Dipi Toppo (1st, 7th), Mahima Choudhary (20th) and Ajmina Kujur (30th) were on target
articles.content:
India continued their unbeaten run in the Women’s Asian Hockey 5s World Cup Qualifier after registering a hard-fought 5-4 win over Thailand in their third match of the tournament here on Sunday.
